column1: Q1: What gender do you identify with?
column4: Q3: What is your race? (white, black, latino, asian, other)
column6: Q4: What is your highest level of education? (High school or less, Some college, College degree, Graduate degree)
column8: Q5: In politics today, do you consider yourself a Democrat, a Republican, or Independent?
column9: Q6: Would you say you are liberal, conservative, or moderate?
column10: Q7: Do you approve, disapprove, or neither approve nor disapprove of how Donald Trump is handling his job as president? (for "approve" or "disapprove," probe: strongly or somewhat?)
column11: Q8: How often do you worry about your financial situation? (very often, somewhat often, or not very often)
column12: Q9: I'd like you to think about vote counting throughout the country. Going into the 2018 midterm elections, are you confident that votes nationwide will be counted fairly? (if [yes] probe: and would you say you are very confident or somewhat confident?)
column13: Q10: Would you support a voting system in which people could choose their first choice candidate, their second choice candidate, their third choice candidate, and so on?
column14: Q11: If you had to guess, do you think America will elect a woman president in the next 25 years?
column15: Q12: Do you think Americans will have universal, guaranteed healthcare in the next 25 years?
column16: Q13: If you had to guess, do you think humanity will survive the next hundred years?
column17: Q14: If Q13 = Yes... And do you think humanity will survive the next thousand years?
column18: Q15: What about America? Do you think America will survive the next hundred years?
column19: Q16: If Q15 = Yes... And do you think America will survive the next thousand years?
column20: Q17: How likely is it that Donald Trump will be re-elected in 2020? (Very likely, somewhat likely, not at all likely)
column21: Q18: How likely is it that Donald Trump will use a nuclear weapon during his time in office? (very likely, somewhat likely, not at all likely)
column22: Q19: If you had to guess, do you think America will go to war with Russia in the next 50 years?
column23: Q20: And if you had to guess, do you think America will go to war with China in the next 50 years?
column24: Q21: Do you think your generation will leave behind a better world for the next generation, or a worse world?
